Ref : 118050918153964 

Symptom : Customer unable to do the Authentication on their SFX with configured AAD 

while looking at the traces, I do noticed this, where user is assigned to ‘ReadWriteUser’ group, and according to the https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/service-fabric/service-fabric-cluster-creation-via-arm#assign-users-to-roles, it should be assigned to ‘ReadOnly’, so it looks like customer not followed the article correctly, and in this scenario it break due to the wrong role assignment. Please suggest the customer to fix their configuration setting, and let me know if you need any further assistance on this issue.
 
 
 
